xmlData.description:
Xml document with root element Root, and sub-elements with user specified names and value attribute (key value pairs).
For example: 
&lt;Root&gt;
    &lt;Site Value="01" /&gt;
    &lt;ChangedDate Value="2019-01-01 13:55:00"/&gt;
&lt;/Root&gt;
Root may also contain a WSBF (WATS Standard BOM Format) document

